cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques using deep learning algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of convolutional neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of deep learning techniques for image processing and analysis also falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of split Bregman technique, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper involves the use of video processing techniques, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
